      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.211-2</ph> Availability of Specifications,
Standards, and Data Item Descriptions Listed in the Acquisition
Streamlining and Standardization Information System (ASSIST).</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3140e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed
in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="11.204.dita#FAR_11_204"
                     base="i1114299"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">11.204</xref>(b)</ph>, insert
the following provision:</p>
         <p id="d3139e15" outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Availability of Specifications, Standards,
and Data Item Descriptions Listed in the Acquisition Streamlining and
Standardization Information System (ASSIST) (Jul 2021)</p>
         <ol id="d3105e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3140e19" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> Most
unclassified Defense specifications and standards may be downloaded
from the following ASSIST websites:</p>
               <ol id="d3105e35" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e25" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> ASSIST (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref "> https://assist.dla.mil/online/start/</xref>);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e33" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Quick Search
(<xref href="http://quicksearch.dla.mil/"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">http://quicksearch.dla.mil/</xref>).
                     </p>
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d3140e40">
                         
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3140e43" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Documents
not available from ASSIST may be ordered from the Department of
Defense Single Stock Point (DoDSSP) by—</p>
               <ol id="d3105e83" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e49" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> Using the
ASSIST Shopping Wizard (<xref href="https://assist.dla.mil/wizard/index.cfm"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">https://assist.dla.mil/wizard/index.cfm</xref>);</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e57" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Phoning
the DoDSSP Customer Service Desk (215) 697-2179, Mon-Fri, 0730 to
1600 EST; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3140e62" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> Ordering
from DoDSSP, Building 4, Section D, 700 Robbins Avenue, Philadelphia,
PA 19111-5094, Telephone (215) 697-2667/2179, Facsimile (215) 697-1462.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofprovision" class="- topic/p ">(End of provision)</p>
